{"prompt": "Design a homepage for a non-profit organization. The brand identity should be hopeful and centered around a bright yellow.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Hopeful Futures - Non-Profit Organization</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #333333;\n            background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Bright yellow primary color */\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .logo {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #333333;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 25px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: #333333;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: #555555;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700, #FFE066); /* Gradient using primary yellow */\n            color: #333333;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            min-height: 70vh;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.1;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            max-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: #FFC107; /* Slightly darker yellow for contrast */\n            color: #333333;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .button:hover {\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Back to primary yellow on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            max-width: 960px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: #333333;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n\n        .section h2::after {\n            content: '';\n            display: block;\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 4px;\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Yellow accent under titles */\n            margin: 15px auto 0;\n            border-radius: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .about {\n            background-color: #FDFDFD; /* Very light secondary color */\n        }\n\n        .about p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        .impact-grid {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .impact-item {\n            background-color: #FFFFFF;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);\n            width: calc(33% - 40px);\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border-top: 5px solid #FFD700; /* Yellow border accent */\n        }\n\n        .impact-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .impact-item h3 {\n            color: #333333;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .impact-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #555555;\n        }\n\n        .cta-bottom {\n            background-color: #FFD700; /* Primary yellow for the final CTA */\n            padding: 60px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #333333;\n        }\n\n        .cta-bottom h2 {\n            font-size: 2.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 25px;\n        }\n        \n        .cta-bottom h2::after {\n            background-color: #333333; /* Dark accent for the yellow background */\n        }\n\n        .cta-bottom p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333333;\n            color: #FFFFFF;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive Design */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            header {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n\n            nav ul {\n                margin-top: 15px;\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n\n            nav ul li {\n                margin: 10px 0;\n            }\n\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n\n            .section h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n\n            .impact-grid {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n\n            .impact-item {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n\n            .cta-bottom h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <a href=\"#\" class=\"logo\">Hopeful Futures</a>\n        <nav>\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#home\">Home</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#impact\">Our Impact</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#donate\">Donate</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n        <section id=\"home\" class=\"hero\">\n            <h1>Bringing Light and Hope to Every Corner</h1>\n            <p>We are dedicated to creating a brighter future through education, empowerment, and community support. Join us in making a real difference.</p>\n            <a href=\"#donate\" class=\"button\">Donate Now</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section about\">\n            <h2>Our Mission</h2>\n            <p>Hopeful Futures is a non-profit organization committed to fostering sustainable change and improving lives in underserved communities. We believe in the power of collective action and the resilience of the human spirit. Our work focuses on providing access to essential resources, promoting lifelong learning, and building stronger, more vibrant communities.</p>\n            <a href=\"#impact\" class=\"button\">Learn More</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"impact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>See Our Impact</h2>\n            <p>Every donation, every volunteer hour, every act of kindness contributes to the profound change we create together. Here\u2019s how we're making a difference:</p>\n            <div class=\"impact-grid\">\n                <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                    <h3>Education Programs</h3>\n                    <p>Providing scholarships, school supplies, and educational workshops to children and adults.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                    <h3>Community Development</h3>\n                    <p>Supporting local initiatives, building infrastructure, and creating safe spaces for growth.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"impact-item\">\n                    <h3>Health & Wellness</h3>\n                    <p>Ensuring access to basic healthcare, nutritional support, and wellness education.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"donate\" class=\"cta-bottom\">\n            <h2>Your Support Creates Hope</h2>\n            <p>Every contribution, no matter the size, helps us continue our vital work and bring hope to those who need it most. Stand with us.</p>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"button\">Make a Donation</a>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Hopeful Futures. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}